        "content": "**AEGIS Forecast Drift — Shape** · Governed read-only **V2** snapshot via datasource `aegis-forecast-drift-csv`. Curve / profile divergence between forecast versions (`shape_drift_score`, governed family weight **40%**). Every signal is **computable** for shape (non-empty `shape_drift_score`), so **coverage** is 100% of the filtered universe. KPIs, the details table and run panels honor all five shared filters (Forecast Key · Forecast Version · Region · Drift Status · Run ID); the drift trend intentionally ignores Forecast Version to keep the full historical series."
